These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, july, june
1. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in june##2
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Birthday   | may | june | september | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, epic, satire, mystery
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | mystery | fantasy | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, writer, engineer, chef
1. the chef is on the right of the designer##1
2. the engineer is between the writer and the chef##2
3. the designer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Job   | designer | chef | engineer | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, lemonade, milk
1. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking iced-tea##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage   | milk | coffee | lemonade | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goat, turtle, fish
1. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the goat##2
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2    |   3   |     4     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | goat | turtle | fish |

 #################################

 
