.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, canasta, go
1. the person playing whist is between the person playing canasta and the person playing bridge##2
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Game   | canasta | whist | bridge | go |

 